data.description: Cozy 3 Bed, 2.5 Bath Home on 2.5 Acres! This gem boasts a 50'x32', 2+car garage, with a half bath and room for 3 vehicles, a fenced-in dog run, RV hookups, UGS and a sprinkler system for your yard and garden. Enjoy a recently remodeled master bathroom, updated flooring, and a modern kitchen. Fresh paint throughout the entire house. Step outside to a cozy covered front deck and a walkway leading to an outdoor fire pit. With 2 wood-burning stoves (main house and garage), you'll stay warm in the winter. Plus, it's close to hunting and river access for fishing. Plenty of space for horses, goats, or your dream outdoor lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity!
